text: USS Florida (SSBN-728/SSGN-728), an cruise missile submarine, is the sixth vessel of the United States Navy to be named for the U.S. state of Florida. She was commissioned with the hull designation of SSBN-728; with her conversion to a cruise missile submarine, from a ballistic missile submarine, she was re-designated SSGN-728. ==References== Category:Submarines of the United States Navy
title: USS Florida (SSGN-728)
